    <p class="center s16"><a href="/help">¿Cómo funciona?</a></p>
    <p class="center s16"><a href="/signup">Regístrate ahora</a></p>
    <% when 'en' %>
    <p class="center s24"><span class="redb">tabelia</span> is your <br /><span class="u">virtual art gallery</span><br/><span class="red">open to the world</span><br/> where anybody is able to <br />present, sell and/or buy <br /> reproductions of the published pictures.<br/></p>
    <p class="center s16">Take a look, <br /><span class="red">and begin enjoying ART.</span></p>
    <p class="center s16"><a href="/help">How this works?</a></p>
    <p class="center s16"><a href="/signup">Join Now!</a></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<% end %>
